p.k: A group of vicious geese arrive at the park and harass the visitors! Mordecai and Rigby think they know some old friends that can help… / A potentially fatal sandwich could be the end of Benson, unless his finds find him a cure! / The leader of an old, hit band who disappeared is said to be living in the park near Mordecai and Rigby, so they try to reunite his old band mates! / After an awkward attempt at a kiss between Mordecai and Margaret, Mordecai faces an ultimatum; kiss Margaret by Friday or wear a diaper for a week…
